## Enabling Self-Evolution

**To enable globally:**
1. Edit this file's frontmatter: `alwaysApply: true`
2. Create `.cursor/evolution/config.json` with desired settings
3. System will start passive analysis after next substantial work

**To enable for one session:**
1. User says "enable self-evolution for this session"
2. Agent activates evolution mode temporarily
3. Deactivates at end of session

**To run one-time analysis:**
1. User says "run evolution analysis"
2. Agent runs Phases 1-4 without enabling ongoing monitoring
3. User can accept/reject proposals as normal
